Subject: drm/i915: add vlv_pipe_to_phy() helper to replace DPIO_PHY()
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 9fda18c2c32a42e6c9fb68893b9628d6a5319555
